Use macOS keyboard mapping when __APPLE__ is defined

These key definitions are taken from Events.h in Carbon.framework, with
the exception of the Windows application key which I tested manually.

Note that F13-F15 are equivalent to Print Screen, Scroll Lock, and Pause
according to SDL.
